pull_request.body:
- Created a new modal component (formio-modal-dialog) to create modals based on Form.io;
- Created a type for the Form.io form to stop declaring it as any (`FormIOForm`). For backward compatibility some parameters were declared as `(forms: any[] | FormIOForm[])`;
- Email notifications adjusted;
- **Uploaded methods moved to the specific student/AEST controllers and upload/download logic centralized on the controller service**. This caused many changes but this will also make the upcoming ticket to reorganize the student API easier.
- Many file uploads DTOs renamed but not moved yet;
- Added a new file origin `Ministry` to be defined on the Ministry uploads a file to the student account;
- Added a new button to the Ministry upload files to students, as shown below.

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/61259237/168900011-9d6488c5-9e05-4054-9c14-608251d21518.png)

- Modal adjusted to me more like the one on Figma: icon removed, title styles adjusted, added dividers, added spaces, as shown below.

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/61259237/168912117-9e0e8ac4-4a4b-4856-a177-f7a99c538f1d.png)

- Created a new are on Students to allow the visualization of the files sent by the Ministry, as shown below.

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/61259237/168926285-ce4b75ba-4da7-4b8f-9891-ed90f8d02eca.png)

- Notification email 

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/61259237/168926965-e5d89ddc-f220-4619-9df0-f6eddb841ba5.png)

